title: 162. Mother's Day Special with Lisa Ireland, Minnie Darke & Sandie Docker
itunes:author: Words and Nerds: Authors, books and literature.
itunes:summary:
Mother's Day Special with Lisa Ireland, Minnie Darke & Sandie Docker.

We chat about what Mother's Day means to them, the invisibility of women as we age, the mothers we pick up along the way and the importance of multigenerational relationships between women.
